title: Weaver's Draft Book (Germany), 1805
description: Small, oblong book covered in decorated end papers with vellum corners and back and remains of leather tabs to tie. Contains weaving graphs in colors of red and black and charts. Simple geometric designs.

tombstone.epitaph: Weaver's Draft Book (Germany), 1805; leather, vellum, paper; H x W: 19 × 16 cm (7 1/2 × 6 5/16 in.); 1953-119-2
